Package org.jreliability.bdd.javabdd

Class JBDD<T>

java.lang.Object
org.jreliability.bdd.javabdd.JBDD<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the variables
All Implemented Interfaces:
BDD<T>
public class JBDD<T> extends Object implements BDD<T>
The JBDD is a BDD based on the JavaBDD standard java implementation.
